  Alerts → Slack webhook or PagerDuty

Critical alerts (PagerDuty / immediate):
  - Kill switch activated
  - Daily loss > 1% NAV (warning at 1%, kill at 2%)
  - Engine offline > 30 seconds
  - P99 latency > 1ms (degraded performance warning)
  - Any order placed as Taker (fee structure violated)

Non-critical alerts (Slack daily digest):
  - Total trades today
  - Net P&L today
  - RN1 trade count today
  - Fill rate summary
